td.p:
Under Article 14(1) of Council Directive 2006/112/EC of 28 November 2006 on the common system of value added tax (
OJ 2006 L 347, p. 1
), as amended by Council Directive 2008/8/EC of 12 February 2008 (
OJ 2008 L 44, p. 11
) (‘the VAT Directive’), ‘“supply of goods” shall mean the transfer of the right to dispose of tangible property as owner’.
